medications.name: Sertraline
medications.response: Minimal/Poor response noted after 4 weeks of treatment.

changes_made.rationale: Inadequate therapeutic response (persistent *anhedonia*, *early morning awakening*, *guilt*) after 4 weeks at 50mg; escalating to 100mg daily to reach a therapeutic level, given severity (*F33.1*).
changes_made.details: Increase dose from 50mg daily to 100mg daily.
